data.description: Discover the charm of this ranch-style home tucked away in prestigious Glenwood Estates, just a leisurely stroll from Chestnut Hill Schools. Boasting three bedrooms and a bonus fourth bedroom in the finished basement, this home offers versatility and ample space. The primary suite is a haven of comfort with its attached bath and generously sized closet. Elegant hardwood floors grace the interior, complemented by a fresh coat of paint throughout, lending a timeless and sophisticated appeal. This residence is move-in ready, providing an immediate opportunity to experience the epitome of stylish and comfortable living. Don't miss the chance to make this your home!
